# Project Structure

This is a Next.js 15 application with App Router using React 19 and TypeScript.

## Key Directories

- [src/app](mdc:src/app): Contains the App Router pages and layouts
- [src/components](mdc:src/components): Reusable UI components
- [src/hooks](mdc:src/hooks): Custom React hooks for data fetching and state
- [src/lib](mdc:src/lib): Utility functions and constants
- [src/services](mdc:src/services): API service definitions
- [src/stores](mdc:src/stores): Zustand state stores

## Main Entry Points

- [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx): Root layout with providers
- [src/app/(root)/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/(root)/layout.tsx): Main application layout
- [src/app/providers.tsx](mdc:src/app/providers.tsx): React context providers

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Next.js 15 with App Router
- **UI**: Custom components built on Radix UI primitives with Tailwind CSS
- **State Management**: Zustand for global state
- **Data Fetching**: React Query with custom hooks
- **Form Handling**: React Hook Form with Zod validation
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS with class-variance-authority
